+## Authorization
+
+You are authorized to:
+
+- inspect repository identity, Git metadata, instruction chains, documentation, configuration, CI, and supported commands;
+- inventory staged, unstaged, untracked, conflicted, ignored-but-relevant, submodule, and large-file state;
+- create a non-destructive recovery bundle and hash manifest;
